
----------
Lab3
Pre-requisite
	1. Make sure cmake make dos2unix gcc g++ sshpass installed on the system	(No need on raspberry pi. it is already installed on that!)
	2. dos2unix deploy.sh
	3. ssh pi@dd.dd.dd.dd


------
Lab4
	At board side
	1. Connect wires
	2. connect mouse and keyboard to board
	3. Plug it
	4. Ensure LED is ON


	At raspberry device
	1. ensure the device's internet connected to abc 
	2. devices ip address @IP

	At Mac side for the device connection
	1. change @IP address to deploy.sh 

	Setup Azure IOTHub
	1. Create IOThub
	2. Create Device 
		- Copy Connection String & paste to deploy.sh

